| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-5863 — Recovery Inhibition (devman)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ed447079-eed0-53a2-a7a9-0c472bcd1b70"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
